message.kamenridercraft.zi_o_rider_2: §aYou have witnessed the moment that he inherits yet another Rider's power!
message.kamenridercraft.zi_o_ii: §aThe one who surpasses the power of all Riders, the king of time who will rule over the past and the future! And his name is Kamen Rider Zi-O II!
message.kamenridercraft.zi_o_ii_2: §aWe have borne witness to the advent of a new history!
message.kamenridercraft.zi_o_trinity: §aThe power of three Riders have apparently gathered. The time monarch who will possibly create the future. And his name is Kamen Rider Zi-OTrinity! This is the moment a new history was created!
message.kamenridercraft.zi_o_trinity_2: §aProstrate yourselves! We are known as Zi-OTrinity. The Demon King Zi-O along with his two underlings. Geiz and Woz. By combining our powers, we'll become the future King of Time!
message.kamenridercraft.grand_zi_o: §aNo... words are no longer necessary... You must simply bask in this moments!
message.kamenridercraft.ohma_zi_o: §aThe ultimate time king who reigns over the time and space, and reigning over the past and future. His name is Ohma Zi-O!
message.kamenridercraft.ohma_zi_o_2: §aWe are now reaching the last page of history itself!
message.kamenridercraft.zi_o_ohma_form: §aThe one to inherit the power of the great demon king, the king of the end times who will rule over all eras! And his name is Kamen Rider Zi-O! This is the advent of his OhmaForm!
message.kamenridercraft.geiz_revive: §aThe one who'll guide us to the new future by smiting all evil, Il Salvatore! His name is Kamen Rider GeizRevive!
message.kamenridercraft.geiz_revive_2: §aRight now, we have witnessed the advent of a True Savior!
message.kamenridercraft.geiz_majesty: §aThe true savior who shines a light to take back the future and protect us from darkness! And his name is Kamen Rider GeizMajesty!
message.kamenridercraft.geiz_majesty_2: §aYou have witnessed his time of advent!
message.kamenridercraft.woz: §aThe reader of the past and the future. The prophet who will write the proper timeline. And his name is Kamen Rider Woz!
message.kamenridercraft.woz_2: §aThis is the first page of a new history!
message.kamenridercraft.wozgingafinaly: §aThe universe's strongest GingaFinaly! Since it's an emergency, I'll keep it short.
message.kamenridercraft.zero_one: §aHe is the symbol of the new Reiwa Era. And his name is Kamen Rider Zero-One!
